2000년 COSKA 골프 대회

다음과 같이 정기 골프대회를 개최하오니 많은 참가를 바랍니다.

Coska has reserved 40 tee-off times at Gormley Greens, please let us know by Aug 18 if you would like to play.  Please note that we are working on a first come, first serve basis, so reserve your spot quickly.


Date    : Aug 26, 2000
Time    : 12:45 PM
Place   : Gormley Green
Fee     : $ 60.00 includes dinner + prizes
Contact Persons : Dave Park(720-8253), Simon Lee(226-2228)
